IMPORTANT: THE DEMO REQUIRES THE HOUSEHOLD OBJECT DATABASE TO BE INSTALLED.

PICK AND PLACE DEMO INSTRUCTIONS
TERMINAL 1: roscore
TERMINAL 2: roslaunch longhorn_object_manipulation fast_demo_app_prerequisites.launch
TERMINAL 3: roslaunch longhorn bringup.launch
TERMINAL 4: rosrun rviz rviz, open config file in longhorn_object_recognition packages
TERMINAL 5: (from longhorn_object_manipulation) ./bin/fast_demo_app_swri

ROBOT INSTRUCTIONS
1. Turn ON
2. Place in TEACH mode
3. Initialize Robot Gripper (Set Universal OUT#0033 to TRUE, Hold INTERLOACK + SELECT)
4. Place in PLAY mode.

 
